\c 41
\s UJosefa uchasisa amaphupho kaFaro
\p
\v 1 Kwasekusithi ekupheleni kweminyaka emibili egcweleyo\x + 27.44.\x* uFaro waphupha; khangela-ke, emi emfuleni.
\v 2 Khangela-ke, emfuleni kwakhuphuka amankomokazi ayisikhombisa, ekhangeleka emahle, enonile enyameni; adla emihlangeni\x + 41.18. Jobe 8.11.\x*.
\v 3 Khangela-ke, amanye amankomokazi ayisikhombisa akhuphuka emfuleni emva kwawo, ekhangeleka kubi, ecakile enyameni; ema eduze lamankomokazi ekhunjini lomfula.
\v 4 Amankomokazi akhangeleka kubi acakileyo enyameni adla amankomokazi akhangeleka kuhle anonileyo. UFaro wasephaphama.
\v 5 Walala futhi, waphupha ngokwesibili; khangela-ke, kwakhahlela izikhwebu eziyisikhombisa ehlangeni linye, ezigcweleyo zilungile.
\v 6 Khangela-ke, izikhwebu eziyisikhombisa ezicakileyo, zihangulwe ngumoya wempumalanga, zakhahlela emva kwazo.
\v 7 Izikhwebu ezicakileyo zaginya izikhwebu ezipheleleyo ezigcweleyo. UFaro wasephaphama, khangela-ke, kwakuliphupho.
\v 8 Kwasekusithi ekuseni umoya wakhe wakhathazeka\x + Hlab. 77.4. Dan. 2.1,3.\x*; wathumela wabiza izangoma zonke zeGibithe lazo zonke izazi zayo\x + 41.24. Eks. 7.11,22. Dan. 1.20; 2.2; 4.7. Mat. 2.1.\x*. UFaro wazilandisela iphupho lakhe; kodwa kwakungekho esasingamchasisela wona uFaro.
\p
\v 9 Induna yabaphathinkezo yasikhuluma kuFaro isithi: Lamuhla ngiyakhumbula amacala ami.
\v 10 UFaro wazithukuthelela inceku zakhe\x + 40.2,3.\x*, wanginikela esitokisini, endlini yenduna yabalindi\x + 37.36 .\x*, mina lenduna yabaphekizinkwa;
\v 11 njalo saphupha iphupho ngabusuku bunye\x + 40.5.\x*, mina layo. Saphupha, ngamunye njengengcazelo yephupho lakhe.
\v 12 Kwakukhona lapho kanye lathi ijaha umHeberu, inceku yenduna yabalindi; sayilandisela yasichasisela amaphupho ethu, yachasisa ngamunye njengephupho lakhe\x + 40.12.\x*.
\v 13 Kwasekusithi njengokusichasisela kwayo kwaba njalo; mina wangibuyisela esikhundleni sami, yena wamlengisa\x + 40.21,22.\x*.
\p
\v 14 UFaro wasethumela wabiza uJosefa\x + Hlab. 105.20.\x*; bamkhupha emgodini\x + 1 Sam. 2.8. Hlab. 113.7,8.\x* ngokuphangisa\x + Dan. 2.25.\x*\f + \fk ngokuphangisa: \fl Heb. \fq bamgijimisa.\f*; esephucile wafaka ezinye izigqoko, wangena kuFaro.
\v 15 UFaro wasesithi kuJosefa: Ngiphuphile iphupho\x + 40.5.\x*, kakho-ke olichasisayo; njalo mina ngizwile ngawe ukuthi: Usizwa iphupho, uyalichasisa\x + 41.12. Dan. 5.16.\x*.
\v 16 UJosefa wasemphendula uFaro esithi: Kakukho kimi\x + Dan. 2.30.\x*. UNkulunkulu\x + 40.8. Dan. 2.22,28,47.\x* uzaphendula impilakahle kaFaro.
\v 17 UFaro wasekhuluma kuJosefa \add wathi\x + 41.1-7.\x*\add*: Ephutsheni lami, khangela, ngangimi ekhunjini lomfula;
\v 18 njalo khangela, kwakhuphuka emfuleni amankomokazi ayisikhombisa, anonileyo enyameni, akhangeleka emahle, adla emihlangeni.
\v 19 Khangela-ke, amanye amankomokazi ayisikhombisa akhuphuka emva kwawo, ayangekileyo, akhangeleka emabi kakhulu, acakileyo enyameni; angizanga ngiwabone anjengawo ngobubi elizweni lonke leGibithe.
\v 20 Kwathi amankomokazi acakileyo lamabi adla amankomokazi ayisikhombisa okuqala anonileyo.
\v 21 Lapho esengene esiswini sawo, kakubonakalanga ukuthi angenile esiswini sawo, ngoba ekhangeleka kubi njengakuqala. Ngasengiphaphama.
\v 22 Ngasengibona ephutsheni lami, khangela-ke, izikhwebu eziyisikhombisa zikhahlela ehlangeni linye, zigcwele zilungile;
\v 23 njalo khangela, izikhwebu eziyisikhombisa ezitshwabheneyo, ezicakileyo, ezihangulwe ngumoya wempumalanga zakhahlela emva kwazo.
\v 24 Njalo izikhwebu ezicakileyo zaginya izikhwebu eziyisikhombisa ezilungileyo. Njalo ngakulandisela izangoma; kodwa kwakungekho esangichasiselayo\x + 41.8.\x*.
\p
\v 25 UJosefa wasesithi kuFaro: Iphupho likaFaro linye. Lokho uNkulunkulu akwenzayo, umazisile uFaro\x + Dan. 2.45. Isam. 4.1.\x*.
\v 26 Amankomokazi ayisikhombisa alungileyo ayiminyaka eyisikhombisa; lezikhwebu eziyisikhombisa ezilungileyo ziyiminyaka eyisikhombisa. Iphupho linye.
\v 27 Njalo amankomokazi acakileyo lamabi akhuphuka emva kwawo ayiminyaka eyisikhombisa; lezikhwebu eziyisikhombisa ezicakileyo ezihangulwe ngumoya wempumalanga zizakuba yiminyaka eyisikhombisa yendlala\x + 2 Kho. 8.1.\x*.
\v 28 Le yinto engiyikhulume kuFaro \add ukuthi\add*: Lokho uNkulunkulu akwenzayo, ukutshengisile kuFaro\x + 41.25.\x*.
\v 29 Khangela, kuyeza iminyaka eyisikhombisa yenala enkulu elizweni lonke leGibithe\x + 41.47.\x*.
\v 30 Kuzavela iminyaka eyisikhombisa yendlala emva kwayo\x + 41.54.\x*; izakhohlakala-ke inala yonke elizweni leGibithe; njalo indlala izaliqeda ilizwe\x + 47.13.\x*.
\v 31 Njalo inala kayiyikwaziwa elizweni ngenxa yaleyondlala emva kwalokho, ngoba izakuba nzima kakhulu.
\v 32 Njalo ukuthi iphupho liphindwe kabili kuFaro, kungoba into \add le\add* imisiwe nguNkulunkulu\x + Nani 23.19. Isa. 46.10,11.\x*, futhi uNkulunkulu uphangisa ukukwenza.
\v 33 Khathesi-ke uFaro kakhangele indoda eqedisisayo lehlakaniphileyo, ayibeke phezu kwelizwe leGibithe.
\v 34 UFaro kenze \add lokhu\add*, abeke ababonisi phezu kwelizwe, athathe ingxenye yesihlanu yelizwe leGibithe eminyakeni eyisikhombisa yenala.
\v 35 Kababuthe konke ukudla kwaliminyaka elungileyo ezayo, njalo kababuthelele amabele ngaphansi kwesandla sikaFaro\x + 41.48.\x*, kube yikudla emizini, bawagcine.
\v 36 Njalo ukudla kuzakuba yisiphala selizwe okweminyaka eyisikhombisa yendlala ezakuba khona elizweni leGibithe, ukuze ilizwe lingabhujiswa\f + \fk lingabhujiswa: \fl Heb. \fq lingaqunywa.\f* yindlala.
\s Ukuphakanyiswa kukaJosefa
\p
\v 37 Njalo into le yabanhle emehlweni kaFaro lemehlweni ezinceku zakhe zonke.
\v 38 UFaro wasesithi encekwini zakhe: Singamthola yini onjengaye, indoda okuyo uMoya kaNkulunkulu\x + Nani 27.18. Dan. 4.8,18; 5.11,14; 6.3.\x*?
\v 39 UFaro wasesithi kuJosefa: Njengalokhu uNkulunkulu ekwazisile konke lokhu, kakho oqedisisayo lohlakaniphileyo njengawe.
\v 40 Wena uzakuba phezu kwendlu yami\x + Hlab. 105.21. Seb. 7.10.\x*, njalo emlonyeni wakho bonke abantu bami bazabuswa\f + \fk bazabuswa: \fl Heb. \fq bazakwanga.\f*; kuphela esihlalweni sobukhosi ngizakuba mkhulu kulawe.
\v 41 UFaro wasesithi kuJosefa: Khangela, ngikubekile phezu kwelizwe lonke leGibithe.
\v 42 UFaro wasekhupha indandatho yakhe elophawu lwakhe esandleni sakhe, wayifaka esandleni sikaJosefa\x + Esta 3.10; 8.2,8,10.\x*, wamgqokisa izigqoko zelembu elicolekileyo kakhulu\x + Esta 8.15.\x*, wamgaxa iketane legolide entanyeni\x + Hez. 16.11. Dan. 5.7,29.\x*.
\v 43 Wamhambisa enqoleni yesibili ayelayo; njalo bamemeza\x + Esta 6.9.\x* phambi kwakhe \add besithi\add*: Guqani! Ngokunjalo wambeka phezu kwelizwe lonke leGibithe\x + 42.6; 45.8,9,26.\x*.
\v 44 UFaro wasesithi kuJosefa: NginguFaro; kodwa ngaphandle kwakho kakho ozaphakamisa isandla sakhe loba unyawo lwakhe elizweni lonke leGibithe.
\v 45 UFaro wasemutha ibizo likaJosefa uZafenathi-Paneya\f + \fk uZafenathi-Paneya: \fl okuyikuthi, \fq umembuli wezimfihlo.\f*. Wamnika uAsenathi, indodakazi kaPotifera umpristi weOni, ukuthi abe ngumka\add khe\add*. UJosefa wasephuma wadabula elizweni leGibithe.
\p
\v 46 Njalo uJosefa wayeleminyaka engamatshumi amathathu mhla esima phambi kukaFaro inkosi yeGibithe\x + 1 Sam. 16.21. 1 Kho. 12.6,8. Dan. 1.19.\x*. UJosefa wasephuma esuka ebusweni bukaFaro, wadabula ilizwe lonke leGibithe.
\v 47 Umhlaba wathela ngezandla ezigcweleyo eminyakeni eyisikhombisa yenala.
\v 48 Waseqoqa konke ukudla kweminyaka eyisikhombisa eyayiselizweni leGibithe, wabeka ukudla emizini; ukudla kwensimu ezingelezele lowo lalowomuzi wakubeka kuwo.
\v 49 UJosefa wasebuthelela amabele njengetshebetshebe lolwandle, aba manengi kakhulu, waze wayekela ukubala, ngoba ayengelanani\x + 22.17. Hlu. 7.12. 1 Sam. 13.5. Hlab. 78.27.\x*.
\p
\v 50 Wasezalelwa uJosefa amadodana amabili\x + 46.20; 48.5.\x*, ungakafiki umnyaka wendlala, amzalela wona uAsenathi indodakazi kaPotifera umpristi\f + \fk umpristi: \fl kumbe, \fq induna.\f* weOni.
\v 51 UJosefa wasebiza ibizo\x + 4.25; 26.7; 32.30; 41.52. Eks. 18.4.\x* lezibulo \add wathi\add* nguManase\f + \fk uManase: \fl okuyikuthi, \fq ukukhohlwa.\f*, \add wathi\add*: Ngoba uNkulunkulu ungenze ukuthi ngikhohlwe konke ukuhlupheka kwami lendlu yonke kababa.
\v 52 Lebizo leyesibili walibiza \add wathi\add* nguEfrayimi\f + \fk uEfrayimi: \fl okuyikuthi, \fq ukuba lezithelo.\f*, \add wathi\add*: Ngoba uNkulunkulu ungenze ukuthi ngibe lezithelo elizweni lokuhlupheka kwami.
\p
\v 53 Kwasekuphela iminyaka eyisikhombisa yenala eyayiselizweni leGibithe.
\v 54 Kwasekuqala ukufika iminyaka eyisikhombisa yendlala\x + Hlab. 105.16. Seb. 7.11.\x*, njengoba uJosefa wayetshilo\x + 41.30.\x*. Kwasekusiba khona indlala emazweni wonke, kodwa elizweni lonke leGibithe kwakukhona isinkwa.
\v 55 Kwathi ilizwe leGibithe lonke selilamba, abantu bakhala ngesinkwa kuFaro. UFaro wasesithi kuwo wonke amaGibithe: Yanini kuJosefa, lenze lokho alitshela khona.
\v 56 Kwathi sekulendlala ebusweni belizwe lonke, uJosefa wavula zonke iziphala\f + \fk iziphala: \fl Heb. \fq konke okwakulolutho.\f*, wathengisela\x + 42.6.\x* amaGibithe; indlala-ke yaba lamandla elizweni leGibithe.
\v 57 Lonke ilizwe lafika eGibithe, ukuthenga, kuJosefa, ngoba indlala yayilamandla emhlabeni wonke\x + 41.54,56.\x*.
